<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Delete Account</title>
</head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px;">
    <div
        style="max-width: 500px; margin: auto; background: #ffffff; padding: 25px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">

        <h2 style="color: #333; margin-bottom: 10px;">Reset Your Password</h2>

        <p style="color: #555; font-size: 14px;">
            We received a request to delete your account. Click the button below to confirm.
        </p>

        <a href="<%= link %>"
            style="display: inline-block; margin: 20px 0; padding: 12px 20px; background-color: #2d89ef; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold;">
            Delete Account
        </a>

        <p style="color: #777; font-size: 13px;">
            This link will expire in <strong>20 minutes</strong>.
        </p>

        <p style="color: #777; font-size: 13px;">
            If the button doesn’t work, copy and paste this link into your browser:
        </p>

        <p style="word-break: break-all; color: #2d89ef; font-size: 12px;">
            <%= link %>
        </p>

        <hr style="margin: 20px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee;" />

        <p style="color: #999; font-size: 12px;">
            If you didn’t request for account delete, you can safely ignore this email.
        </p>

    </div>

</body>

</html>